íŸ@ffae292c73d9341b6cb177a369161340ffdf29fd82bcee8f1eda838bb134dcd3⁄ÖTitle: title: path exists
Path: Examples
Content:
Check if a file exists.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '/home/joe/todo.txt' | path exists
false

```
Check if files in list exist.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [ /home/joe/todo.txt, /home/doe/todo.txt ] | path exists
