íŸ@f444493c8782a4e250ff207c129ad4305c7488002064d4eb8ee25ee043e60f11⁄.Title: title: path exists
Path: Notes
Content:
This only checks if it is possible to either 
``open``
 or 
``cd``
 to the given path.

If you need to distinguish dirs and files, please use 
``path type``
.

Also note that if you don't have a permission to a directory of a path, false will be returned
